sequenceDiagram
    participant A as Activity
    participant VG as 外层 ViewGroup<br/>(如 ScrollView)
    participant V as 子 View<br/>(如 Button)

    Note over A,V: === ACTION_DOWN ===
    A->>VG: dispatchTouchEvent(DOWN)
    VG->>VG: onInterceptTouchEvent(DOWN) → false
    VG->>V: child.dispatchTouchEvent(DOWN)
    V->>V: onTouchEvent(DOWN) → true
    V-->>VG: return true
    Note over VG: mFirstTouchTarget = View

    Note over A,V: === ACTION_MOVE (VG 决定拦截) ===
    A->>VG: dispatchTouchEvent(MOVE)
    VG->>VG: onInterceptTouchEvent(MOVE) → true (拦截!)
    Note over VG: 发现需要拦截
    VG->>V: dispatchTouchEvent(ACTION_CANCEL)
    Note over V: 收到 CANCEL<br/>释放按压状态/取消长按
    V-->>VG: return
    Note over VG: 清除 mFirstTouchTarget = null

    Note over A,V: === 后续 ACTION_MOVE / UP ===
    A->>VG: dispatchTouchEvent(MOVE)
    Note over VG: mFirstTouchTarget == null<br/>不再调用 onInterceptTouchEvent()
    VG->>VG: onTouchEvent(MOVE) → 自己处理 (滚动)

    A->>VG: dispatchTouchEvent(UP)
    VG->>VG: onTouchEvent(UP) → 自己处理 (惯性滚动)
